                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm-1-13a1 1 0 112 0v4a1 1 0 11-2 0V5zm1 9a1.5 1.5 0 100-3 1.5 1.5 0 000 3z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
